34:34.000 --> 34:35.633
- That's great.
- I know.

34:35.667 --> 34:37.500
It's taken a long time to
get there and I'm really happy.

34:37.533 --> 34:39.633
- Do you still take
random drug tests...

34:39.667 --> 34:41.100
- Oh, yeah.
- Mandated by Thomas?

34:41.133 --> 34:42.767
- Mm-hmm, I just
took one the other day.

34:43.000 --> 34:44.000
- Really?

34:44.033 --> 34:46.633
Is there a part of you that

34:46.667 --> 34:49.066
resents taking the drug test,

34:49.100 --> 34:51.600
