34:54.667 --> 34:59.000
- Mm, you know,
I don't really have, I guess,

34:59.033 --> 35:01.467
any resentment,
because I just don't care.

35:01.500 --> 35:03.433
I'll take the test.
I knew I would never fail.

35:03.467 --> 35:06.233
But I will say that
I know it kind of comes

35:06.266 --> 35:09.467
from a place of--like, out of
spite, or whatever with him.

35:09.500 --> 35:14.500
- Is there any element of you
that feels that

35:14.533 --> 35:17.500
the random drug tests
help you stay sober?

35:17.533 --> 35:19.700
- No.
- What's keeping you sober?

35:19.734 --> 35:21.166
- My kids.

35:21.200 --> 35:22.600
- For the most part,
you and Thomas

35:22.633 --> 35:24.500
seemed to get along this season.

35:24.533 --> 35:26.166
What--to what
do you attribute that?

35:26.200 --> 35:28.033
- Being numb to a lot of things

35:28.066 --> 35:29.200
from him, I guess.

35:29.233 --> 35:31.000
And, uh, yeah,
I'm trying to be

35:31.033 --> 35:33.734
you know, a positive person,
or whatever, in his life

35:33.767 --> 35:35.166
with all that's going on.

35:35.200 --> 35:36.767
- Given that he's
still with Ashley,

35:37.000 --> 35:38.500
how hard is that for you?

35:38.533 --> 35:41.667
- Mm, well, I try to just
not think about it,

35:41.700 --> 35:44.033
or her, 'cause I really truly
don't feel like

35:44.066 --> 35:46.734
at the end of the day, she's
going to be around forever.

35:46.767 --> 35:49.233
- How often do you
see her these days?

35:49.266 --> 35:51.033
- I have not
seen or spoken to her

35:51.066 --> 35:53.166
since, uh, the finale.

35:53.200 --> 35:54.767
- Since Patricia's ball?
- Or--since Patricia's ball.

35:55.000 --> 35:57.166
Yeah.
- Really? Wow.

35:57.200 --> 35:59.166
At last year's reunion,
you told us

35:59.200 --> 36:01.166
you didn't have
a large support system,

36:01.200 --> 36:03.266
because it's difficult
for you to trust people.

36:03.300 --> 36:05.166
Would you say
the same thing today?

36:05.200 --> 36:06.600
- Not at all.

36:06.633 --> 36:08.200
I guess after meeting y'all
and, like,

36:08.233 --> 36:09.600
really getting to know you and

36:09.633 --> 36:11.066
you being open to me,
it, like, really

36:11.100 --> 36:12.600
gave me faith in humanity.
[soft laugh]

36:12.633 --> 36:16.066
And I--I don't know,
I've slowly been able to

36:16.100 --> 36:17.200
be vulnerable, I guess.

36:17.233 --> 36:18.600
And, um, yeah.

36:18.633 --> 36:20.734
- I've gotta assume that this is

36:20.767 --> 36:23.033
really a watershed for you,

36:23.066 --> 36:26.266
being able to sit here and
call this group your friends.

36:26.300 --> 36:29.133
- Yeah, um.
- What does that mean to you?

36:29.166 --> 36:32.600
- That that chapter's
finally firmly in the past.

36:32.633 --> 36:34.633
Everyone here
has really given me

36:34.667 --> 36:37.200
an opportunity to be myself

36:37.233 --> 36:40.266
and not feel--I don't know--
I'm sorry, y'all.

36:40.300 --> 36:42.133
I'm like...
- No, you're fine.

36:42.166 --> 36:43.767
- It's just like you got done--
- No, this is awesome.

36:44.000 --> 36:46.033
- Like, I view Kathryn
in such a different light now.

36:46.066 --> 36:49.333
I view you now
as more of a victim.

36:49.367 --> 36:51.000
I do.

36:51.033 --> 36:52.233
- What do you mean "victim"?

36:52.266 --> 36:54.166
- When Thomas met Kathryn,

36:54.200 --> 36:56.600
she was pretty much
still a child.

36:56.633 --> 36:58.166
I think he took
advantage of her.

36:58.200 --> 37:00.100
I do, and I think
he manipulated her

37:00.133 --> 37:03.033
and also manipulated
a lot of us

37:03.066 --> 37:04.700
into being against her.

37:04.734 --> 37:07.500
I think, just personally,
now that I'm a mother,

37:07.533 --> 37:09.734
looking back with
what she went through,

37:09.767 --> 37:12.734
having two kids and being in
the situation that she was in,

37:12.767 --> 37:14.233
and, you know...

37:14.266 --> 37:15.500
- Alone.

37:15.533 --> 37:17.133
And, I mean, I have a husband

37:17.166 --> 37:18.533
and all the support
in the world.

37:18.567 --> 37:20.066
Like, I can't imagine what--

37:20.100 --> 37:21.600
I have so much more empathy
for you now.

37:21.633 --> 37:23.567
And, like, I cannot imagine
what you, um...

37:23.600 --> 37:26.700
[gentle music]

37:26.734 --> 37:28.233
[crying]
I can't imagine

37:28.266 --> 37:30.767
how you have felt,
and I'm really sorry.

37:31.000 --> 37:32.667
♪ ♪

37:32.700 --> 37:34.133
- I appreciate that.
Thank you.

37:34.166 --> 37:35.266
Oh, my God, I'm gonna cry now.
