37:49.767 --> 37:51.467
[dramatic music]

37:51.500 --> 37:53.100
- I appreciate that.
Thank you.

37:53.133 --> 37:54.367
Oh, my God, I'm gonna cry now.
Shoot.

37:54.400 --> 37:57.200
- Sh--, like, God!
- Sh--!

37:57.233 --> 38:00.367
- But it's so true.
- Yeah.

38:00.400 --> 38:02.367
And Thomas is very convincing.

38:02.400 --> 38:04.066
He convinced me of a--

38:04.100 --> 38:07.000
a different life
than perhaps what transpired.

38:07.033 --> 38:09.333
- If you're pregnant,
I'm right there,

38:09.367 --> 38:11.000
everything I got

38:11.033 --> 38:13.000
every dime I've got
in my fortune,

38:13.033 --> 38:15.300
everything is
right there behind you.

38:15.333 --> 38:17.700
I promise you.

38:17.734 --> 38:19.467
- And you believed him.
- Mm-hmm.

38:19.500 --> 38:21.433
- Tell me,
what does that mean to you,

38:21.467 --> 38:23.367
hearing what she said?
Because that was big.

38:23.400 --> 38:25.000
- Yeah.
- And she's really judged you.

38:25.033 --> 38:26.300
- [crying] I have.

38:26.333 --> 38:28.300
I don't want to be around it,
