I just can't imagine what--

38:40.433 --> 38:42.767
what you've been through
as a mom,

38:43.000 --> 38:46.000
and not having
support around you

38:46.033 --> 38:47.667
in that time in your life.

38:47.700 --> 38:50.500
And then to have all the sh--
you had to go through

38:50.533 --> 38:53.166
