38:55.200 --> 38:57.033
It means a lot
to hear that, because

38:57.066 --> 38:59.767
I've had a lot of resentment
and, like, anger, I guess,

39:00.000 --> 39:02.266
because I've felt
like I was treated unfairly.

39:02.300 --> 39:04.266
But I know Thomas
is super convincing.

39:04.300 --> 39:07.033
And to have you say that,
like, finally

39:07.066 --> 39:09.500
gives me affirmation that
I wasn't the crazy one, and...

39:09.533 --> 39:11.433
- No, you were not.
- Now finally you guys see it.

39:11.467 --> 39:13.266
He's showed you guys on his own,

39:13.300 --> 39:15.734
and I knew nature would
take its course or whatever.

39:15.767 --> 39:17.433
I just appreciate being

39:17.467 --> 39:19.700
in a place where you guys
understand me, 'cause I think

39:19.734 --> 39:21.533
feeling so misunderstood
for so long...

39:21.567 --> 39:24.300
- I know.
- Is even--I don't know, but.

39:24.333 --> 39:26.033
- You know, Cameran,
it's interesting 'cause

39:26.066 --> 39:27.333
you described her as "victim,"

39:27.367 --> 39:29.166
but she's flipped that around.
- Yes.

39:29.200 --> 39:31.200
I mean, I think she's grown up.

39:31.233 --> 39:33.033
I mean, she's been through
more than,

39:33.066 --> 39:34.400
I mean, all of us put together.

39:34.433 --> 39:37.166
And the fact that
you're able to sit here

39:37.200 --> 39:41.200
and be so poised and calm
and put-together,

39:41.233 --> 39:44.200
with the pure hell
that you have been through,

39:44.233 --> 39:45.767
I mean, it says a lot about you.

39:46.000 --> 39:47.467
It really does, Kathryn.

39:47.500 --> 39:49.367
It really does,
and I think

39:49.400 --> 39:52.100
in the end, you're
gonna have the last laugh.

39:52.133 --> 39:53.500
And you're gonna
look back on all this,

39:53.533 --> 39:55.033
and it's all gonna make sense.

39:55.066 --> 39:56.400
I really do.

39:56.433 --> 39:58.300
- Hm.
That was nice.

39:58.333 --> 40:00.500
- [crying] That means so much
