seen me grow up, and...

40:06.200 --> 40:07.433
- I know we all, like, you know,

40:07.467 --> 40:09.066
have our differences
and everything,

40:09.100 --> 40:10.200
but, like, for
you especially, like,

40:10.233 --> 40:12.000
we'll always be in your corner.

40:12.033 --> 40:14.400
- [sniffs]
