40:19.633 --> 40:21.400
- You know, like,
all is resolved, almost.

40:21.433 --> 40:23.567
You know.
Um. Yeah.

40:23.600 --> 40:25.166
- Do you feel like
a different person?

40:25.200 --> 40:26.200
- Absolutely.

40:26.233 --> 40:27.500
When I think back to

40:27.533 --> 40:29.500
season one,
or I watch an old episode,

40:29.533 --> 40:32.166
I don't even know that person.

40:32.200 --> 40:35.400
Um, and I became, like, the--a
shell of the person that I was.

40:35.433 --> 40:37.533
But I'm not there anymore.

40:37.567 --> 40:41.333
I'm a different person,
