40:44.433 --> 40:45.500
I'm sorry.
- No...

40:45.533 --> 40:47.333
- What do you feel awful for?

40:47.367 --> 40:49.300
- I just--I don't even
think we know the half of it,

40:49.333 --> 40:51.066
of what she's been put through.

40:51.100 --> 40:53.233
And you do a really good job of

40:53.266 --> 40:56.100
putting on a brave face.
- Thank you, um.

40:56.133 --> 40:57.633
It's kind of like
when you don't have an option,

40:57.667 --> 41:00.166
